name: Inclusion T-shirt. Organic cotton S M L XL mens and womens styles
description:
"Inclusion T"

Everyone could use a little more inclusion is their life! RidgwayInk's first attempt at world peace.

Based on original pen and ink by Matt Ridgway and screen printed by the artist on a natural unbleached organic cotton T-shirt.
Inclusion design is printed on the back of the T and a smaller, simpler design is on the front.
Available in male and female styles
and in these sizes-S,M,L,XL.

Please allow 1 to 2 weeks for delivery.
